Array functions
[PHP > Arrays]
What is the output ?
----
<?php
$base_array = ['red', 'green', 'yellow', 'white'];
$replacements_array = [0 => 'orange', 4 => 'blue'];

$result = array_replace($base_array, $replacements_array);
print_r($result);
----
Array
(
[0] => yellow
[1] => white
[2] => blue
[3] => green
[4] => orange
)
        
An error
 
Array
(
[0] => orange
[1] => green
[2] => yellow
[3] => white
[4] => blue
)

Array
(
[0] => blue
[1] => white
[2] => yellow
[3] => green
[4] => orange
)

